title: Grateful Dead Live at Cal State Dominguez Hills on 1990-05-05
source: Bruel and Kjaer 4011 cardioids as ORTF stereo => Neumann p48v power => Sony TCD-D10 DAT => Sony TC-D5M cassette master (TC-D5M in live recording chain; this analog master is the 24.96 digital master source); From upfront, FOB-DFC; Mics at 6’03”+ being covered by Mike. Knobs and buttons twiddlin’ by Tom D.
